{"tid":1985790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡男子返國外出吃肉骨茶　首宗違居家令判囚6周","createTime":"2020-04-23T11:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T12:41:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1fda89c8026b14ba9633608f2a98e56f301de294","tid":1985790,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200423/s00005/82fab541030b0a0600a01896f2fc5f80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F82fab541030b0a0600a01896f2fc5f80.jpg&h=dff9a6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡的新型冠狀病毒確診個案近日顯著增加，一名男子上月違反居家檢疫令，今日（23日）被判入獄6周，為新加坡首宗因違反居家令被判刑的案件。<br />\n<br />\n任職輔警的34歲男子譚祥生（Alan Tham Xiang Sheng，音譯）於3月23日從緬甸返回新加坡後，接到「居家通告」（SHN），即他須從當日起至4月6日留在家中。<br />\n<br />\n譚祥生當日下午3時許下飛機後，並無立即回家，而是先與女友在樟宜機場的美食街用餐，其後乘車到半島廣場一家兌換店，傍晚時再搭車回家。惟約2小時後再與女友外出，前往海軍部村莊熟食中心吃肉骨茶，隨後去附近超市買東西，約晚上10時才回到家。<br />\n<br />\n據報，譚祥生拍下肉骨茶的照片，上傳到社交媒體，惹網友批評，要求當局嚴查。新加坡移民當局3月25日前往譚祥生家中檢查，譚祥生承認接到居家通告後並無立即回家。他4月16日承認違反《傳染病法》規定。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡2月18日起實施新的居家令措施，違反居家通知者最高刑罰為監禁6個月及罰款一萬新加坡元（約5.4萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡今日公布新增1111宗確診，累計9125宗。為遏止狀病毒散播，總理李顯龍下午宣布，原本5月4日屆滿的封城措施將延至6月1日。<br />\n<br />\n（聯合早報/海峽時報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200423/s00005/1587639990322/%e6%96%b0%e5%8a%a0%e5%9d%a1%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e8%bf%94%e5%9c%8b%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e5%90%83%e8%82%89%e9%aa%a8%e8%8c%b6-%e9%a6%96%e5%ae%97%e9%81%95%e5%b1%85%e5%ae%b6%e4%bb%a4%e5%88%a4%e5%9b%9a6%e5%91%a8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F1587639990322%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%259d%25a1%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e8%25bf%2594%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2590%2583%25e8%2582%2589%25e9%25aa%25a8%25e8%258c%25b6-%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25ae%2597%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%25b1%2585%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e5%2588%25a4%25e5%259b%259a6%25e5%2591%25a8&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6iEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=4c73b44c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200423%2Fs00005%2F1587639990322%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%258a%25a0%25e5%259d%25a1%25e7%2594%25b7%25e5%25ad%2590%25e8%25bf%2594%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2590%2583%25e8%2582%2589%25e9%25aa%25a8%25e8%258c%25b6-%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25ae%2597%25e9%2581%2595%25e5%25b1%2585%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e5%2588%25a4%25e5%259b%259a6%25e5%2591%25a8&h=d1c8382a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200423/s00005/1587639990322/%e6%96%b0%e5%8a%a0%e5%9d%a1%e7%94%b7%e5%ad%90%e8%bf%94%e5%9c%8b%e5%a4%96%e5%87%ba%e5%90%83%e8%82%89%e9%aa%a8%e8%8c%b6-%e9%a6%96%e5%ae%97%e9%81%95%e5%b1%85%e5%ae%b6%e4%bb%a4%e5%88%a4%e5%9b%9a6%e5%91%a8</a>"},{"pid":"4e6c0c5a5a0378a622243de88bc99a2304f400f3","tid":1985790,"uid":60539,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"monkey eat monkey jailed<br />\n不過對比返香港既隔離<br />\n真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"97e6abacd1aa94f05bdb99ada3c045231b87e641","tid":1985790,"uid":230594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁on9<br />\n成日都係FB破案<br />\n利申 FB唔PO相"},{"pid":"907fe610268302d439f0b9d3e1d3958445667d42","tid":1985790,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"應該罰打籐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3665a38eea761a4288adf9fec8040cb7bb175873","tid":1985790,"uid":156542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:07:17.000Z","msg":"柒少陣當幫忙啦<br />\n<br />\n偷食要抹咀都唔撚識"},{"pid":"8339878e1bb99c2b383243e9463a5966a9b0c788","tid":1985790,"uid":187232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T12:41:27.000Z","msg":"Monkey Bone Monkey Tea"}]}